Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:48.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}總是詭辯不好好反省
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不管你了
